                               Subject : LOANS

   collect     Foreclose an overdue loan
  consider     Accept, decline or postpone consideration of a loan
 financial     Show all the outstanding loans in the world
    ledger     Report on outstanding loans
     offer     Offer a loan to another country
     repay     Repay a loan (all or part)
     shark     Purchase defaulted loan

For  info  on  a particular topic, type "info <topic>" where <topic> is one of
the topics listed above.

